{"name": "neowg", "metadata": {"name": "neowg", "version": "1.2.1", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: GNU General Public License v3 (GPLv3)", "License :: Other/Proprietary License", "Operating System :: POSIX :: Linux", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.11", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.12", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3.13"], "home_page": null, "license": "GPLv3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": [], "summary": "Library for working with wireguard configs.", "upload_time": 1732366026}, "documentation": ["# neowg\n\n# \u0412\u0410\u0416\u041d\u041e, \u0411\u0418\u0411\u041b\u0418\u041e\u0422\u0415\u041a\u0410 \u0420\u0410\u0411\u041e\u0422\u0410\u0415\u0422 \u0422\u041e\u041b\u042c\u041a\u041e \u0421\u041e \u0421\u0412\u041e\u0418\u041c \u0424\u041e\u0420\u041c\u0410\u0422\u041e\u041c \u041a\u041e\u041d\u0424\u0418\u0413\u041e\u0412\n\n## \u0423\u0441\u0442\u0430\u043d\u043e\u0432\u043a\u0430\n\n```shell\npip install neowg\n```\n\n## \u041f\u0440\u0438\u043c\u0435\u0440\u044b \u0438\u0441\u043f\u043e\u043b\u044c\u0437\u043e\u0432\u0430\u043d\u0438\u044f:\n\n### \u0421\u043e\u0437\u0434\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043d\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0433\u043e \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0444\u0438\u0433\u0430\n\n```python\nfrom neowg import WgServerConfig\n\nconfig = WgServerConfig.new(\n    server_ip=\"<YOUR_WG_SERVER_IP>\",\n    net_adapter=\"<YOUR_WG_SERVER_NET_ADAPTER>\",\n    clients_count=100,\n) # \u0421\u043e\u0437\u0434\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043e\u0431\u044a\u0435\u043a\u0442\u0430 \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0444\u0438\u0433\u0430\nconfig.dump(\"wg.conf\") # \u0417\u0430\u043f\u0438\u0441\u044c \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0444\u0438\u0433\u0430 \u0432 \u0444\u0430\u0439\u043b\n```\n\n### \u0427\u0442\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0444\u0438\u0433\u0430 \u0438\u0437 \u0444\u0430\u0439\u043b\u0430.\n\n```python\nfrom neowg import WgServerConfig\n\nconfig = WgServerConfig.from_file(\"wg.conf\") # \u0421\u043e\u0437\u0434\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043e\u0431\u044a\u0435\u043a\u0442\u0430 \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0444\u0438\u0433\u0430\n```\n\n### \u0418\u0437\u043c\u0435\u043d\u0435\u043d\u0438\u044f \u043f\u0430\u0440\u044b \u043a\u043b\u044e\u0447\u0435\u0439\n\n```python\nfrom neowg import WgServerConfig\n\nconfig = WgServerConfig.from_file(\"wg.conf\") # \u0421\u043e\u0437\u0434\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043e\u0431\u044a\u0435\u043a\u0442\u0430 \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0444\u0438\u0433\u0430\nconfig.update_keys(\"10.0.0.2\")\nconfig.dump(\"wg.conf\")\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "neowg.wg_server_config", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [{"name": "neowg.wg_server_config.WgServerConfig", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "neowg.wg_server_config.WgServerConfig.new", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cls", "type": {"name": "type", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.type", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Self", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Self", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "clients_count", "type": {"name": "int", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.int", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "Self", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Self", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["\u0421\u043e\u0437\u0434\u0430\u043d\u0438\u0435 \u043d\u043e\u0432\u043e\u0433\u043e \u043a\u043e\u043d\u0444\u0438\u0433\u0430."]}, {"name": "neowg.wg_server_config.WgServerConfig.from_file", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "cls", "type": {"name": "type", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.type", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Self", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Self", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "path", "type": {"name": "Path | str", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Self", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Self", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["\u